Hello there my name is Fitzroy I was born on 7/9/2021 to Nico Pets Litter #4 INFO: Nico Pets are a collection of randomly generated 3D animated wiggly wobbly buddies released exclusively on the Tezos blockchain. ||| DEV LOG:
7-9-2021 Another great day of selling NicoPets! list is updated on nicodaunt.com/nicopets...added more particle effects, different faces/eyes and new/ rare features coming in todays litter! Thanks to everyone who's joined in so far! dm me @nicodaunt if you want to bring your Kalamint NicoPet into HicEtNunc, transfers are free for the next week!||| 7-8-2021 Delightfully stoked on the success of the first two litters of NicoPets. I've recently claimed the domain nicopets.nft, .nfts are still not functional yet, but that will be the place where all nicopet info and archived devlogs will go once its up! For now, check out nicodaunt.com/nicopets for a running list of available nicopets! ||| 7-7-2021 hic et nunc is back up! I'll be randomly dropping NicoPets to both kalamint and hic et nunc throughout the day. Still doing 3-5 pets in each litter so check out https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/NicoPets/creations as well for new pets! ||| As for now there will be 3-5 Nico Pets born daily, look out for new litters on hicetnunc DM me on Instagram or Twitter for more info @nicodaunt
